org.apache.hadoop.fs

接口 Seekable

  • 所有已知实现类:
    BlockDecompressorStream, CompressionInputStream, CryptoFSDataInputStream, DecompressorStream, FSDataInputStream, SplitCompressionInputStream

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
@InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface Seekable
    Stream that permits seeking.

    • 方法概要

      方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      long getPos()
      Return the current offset from the start of the file
      void seek(long pos)
      Seek to the given offset from the start of the file.

    • 方法详细资料

      • seek

        void seek(long pos)
          throws IOException
        Seek to the given offset from the start of the file. The next read() will be from that location. Can't seek past the end of the file.
        抛出:
        IOException

      • getPos

        long getPos()
            throws IOException
        Return the current offset from the start of the file
        抛出:
        IOException
